{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Time for a climb! Take your prehistoric pets on a tower conquering adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Climb alone or compete with other players in asynchronous multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The mighty mammoth and his friends are ready to conquer the spiral stairs of trap ridden castle towers. Finish all levels, beat timed challenges, collect coins and unlock perks &amp; cosmetics and race against the best time of other players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/to_the_top_1.gif?t=1736855667\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Take chances, but do be careful!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sharp spikes, rolling barrels, heavy rocks, falling platforms, fire traps and jumping bombs will block your way, and it is up to your skills, strategy (and of course luck!) to overcome all obstacles. Collect useful tools and abilities on your way up to survive and prosper!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Follow the ghost?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn from the mistakes of your past. You can see the ghostly apparition of your last try on the stairs - follow them, but don't get too comfortable: there is a reason they failed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/to_the_top_2.gif?t=1736855667\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you ready for the challenge ahead?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Single player</strong> - challenge yourself in Time trial, or an NPC opponent in Race mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Asynchronous multiplayer</strong> \u2013 race against real players in Versus mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Perks</